MARKLEY et al.
v.
ROSENBLUM Lutz
v.
Rosenblum S065551, (S065552) Supreme Court of Oregon. May 18, 2018

Having received no timely filed objections, the court certifies to the Secretary of State the Attorney General's second modified ballot title (filed May 10, 2018) for Proposed Initiative Petition No. 28 (2018). ORS 250.085(9).
